17
00:06:52,034 --> 00:07:19,507
from the phrasing and the legal language is great because it's not necessary and stigmatizing. And I think there's a lot of ways we can scrub things from our local laws and our state laws. They just made a big change at the state level to this effect and the Department of Developmental Services

