00:50:45,833 --> 00:51:14,538
to have a test for the next chief of police, you have to have four individuals in the grade below chief of police eligible to take that test. So they didn't have it, and it opened up to lieutenants. So instead of having three candidates eligible and competing for the job, they had an additional nine. So that was 12. It allowed me to compete for the job, and I ended up being a successful candidate, so I think it was the right process. But now, with the change of civil service law, the law only is two.

