And at any given time, you know, a captain, you've got to imagine, is a senior officer, right? They've been around for many, many years. And at any given time, if you only have two qualified candidates, you restrict the amount internally in-house, how many you could have. And it excludes, like, my lieutenants. And a lot of lieutenants do a lot of good work and are qualified to sort of compete for that job.

129
